additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Irritant. Do not swallow. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Causes serious eye irritation. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 131 126; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If swallowed, do not induce vomiting, give 2 glasses of water to drink. In case of contact with eyes and skin, rinse immediately with plenty of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor. If medical advice is needed, have product container or label at hand.
